      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait so u mean its basically just taking the parts from these communities that sell well? that sounds kinda cynical lol. if i want to design something that actually captures that vibe without just being a caricature, what kind of \"energy\" or \"social status\" should the clothes convey? like, when people see this streetwear, what should they automatically think about the person wearing it?",
