      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean about the vibe, but youre making it sound like being \"urban\" is basically synonymous with being from a rough neighborhood or having to be \"hard.\" is there any other side to it? or is the aesthetic fundamentally tied to that kind of struggle and grit to actually be considered \"authentic\" in streetwear?",
